hadiths[23]{hadithnumber,text}:
326,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi biwi mutahra ney ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) kiya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey bachey huye pani sey wuzu karna chaha to unhoney ye baat aap ko batai. aap ney farmaya : tehqiq pani ko koi chiz paleed nahin karti."
327,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke puchha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap bizaa,a key kunwen sey wuzu kartey hain jab ke us kunwen mein kutton ka gosht haiz waley kapdey aur gandagi gir padti hai? aap ney farmaya : pani paak aur paak karney wala hota hai. koi chiz us ko paleed nahin karti."
328,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey guzra jab ke aap bazaa'a key kunwen key pani sey wuzu farma rahey they. mainey kaha : kya aap is pani sey wuzu kartey hain, halanke is mein baaz naa-pasandida gandi cheezen girti rehti hain? aap ney farmaya : is pani ko koi chiz paleed nahin karti."
329,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is pani key barey mein puchha gaya jis par janwer (aur khusoosan) darindey (peeney key liye) aatey jatey rehtey hain? aap ney farmaya : jab pani do matkey ho to wo paleed nahin hota.
330,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke eik dehaati ney masjid mein peshab karna shuru kar diya. kuchh log uski janib uthey to aap ney farmaya is ka peshab na roko. jab wo farigh ho gaya to aap ney pani ka eik dol mangwaya aur peshab par baha diya."
331,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke eik dehaati utha aur us ney masjid mein peshab kar diya. logon ney us ko daantaa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya is ko rehney do aur uskey peshab par eik dol pani baha do. tumhein aasani karney key liye bheja gaya hai, na ke tangi karney key liye."
332,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi aadmi jab ke wo junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho, thehrey pani mein na nahaaey."
333,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, farmatey hain : eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! tehqiq hum samandari safar kartey hain aur apney sath thoda bahut pani ley kar jatey hain. ab agar hum us sey wuzu karen to hum piyasey rahengey. to kya hum samandari pani sey wuzu kar liya karen? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : samandar ka pani paak aur paak karney wala hota hai aur us ka marney wala janwer halal hota hai."
334,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! meri ghaltiyaan barf aur olon key pani sey dho dey. aur merey dil ko ghaltiyon sey is tarah paak saaf farma dey jis tarah tu ney safed kapdey ko mail kuchail sey paak saaf rakha hai."
335,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, farmatey hain : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! mujhey barf, pani aur olon key sath dho kar ghaltiyon sey saaf farma dey."
336,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi key bartan mein kutta munh dal kar piye to usey chahiye ke mashrub ko gira dey aur bartan ko saat dafa dhoey."
337,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kutton ko qatl karney ka hukm diya aur shikar aur bakriyon ki hifazat key liye kutta rakhney ki ijazat di aur farmaya : jab kutta bartan mein munh dal dey to usey saat dafa dho'o aur aathwein dafa usey mitti sey maanjho.
338,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kutton key qatl karney ka hukm diya, farmaya : logon ka kutton sey kya talluq ? aur aap ney shikar aur bakriyon ki hifazat key liye kutta rakhney ki ijazat di aur farmaya : jab kutta bartan mein munh dal dey to us ( bartan ) ko saat dafa dho'o aur aathwein baar mitti sey maanjho. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal ki mukhalifat ki aur kaha : eik dafa mitti key sath (dho'o)."
339,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kutta kisi key bartan mein chaat jaey to wo usey saat dafa dhoey. un mein sey pehli dafa mitti key sath ( dhoey )."
340,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kutta kisi key bartan sey pi jaey to wo usey saat dafa dhoey. un mein sey pehli dafa mitti key sath ( dhoey )."
341,Hazrat Kabsha bint Kaab bin Malik sey marwi hai ke Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) merey paas aaye. mainey unkey liye wuzu ka pani dala. itney main eik billi aai aur us sey peeney lagi. unhoney uskey liye bartan jhuka diya (taake wo achi tarah pi sakey. ) Kabsha ney kaha : chunanche unhoney mujhey dekha ke main ( tajjub sey) dekh rahi hun to wo kehney lagey : aey bhatiji ! tajjub karti hai? mainey kaha : haan ! wo kehney lagey : tehqiq Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : bilashuba ye ( billi ) paleed nahin hai. ye to tum par aaney janey waley ( nokaron aur nokraniyon ) ki tarah hai.
342,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : kabhi-kabhi main eik haddi sey gosht nochti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apna munh mubarak wahin rakhtey jahan mainey rakha tha, halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi. isi tarah mein bartan sey pani peeti to aap apna munh mubarak wahin rakhtey jahan mainey apna munh rakha tha, halanke mein haiz ki haalat mein hoti thi."
343,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein ( nuzool hijaab sey qabl ya Mohrim ) mard aur aurten ikhattey wuzu kar liya kartey they.
344,Hazrat Hakam bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke mard aurat key wuzu (ya ghusl ) sey bachey huye pani key sath wuzu kerey.
345,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, farmati hain : bilashuba wo Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik bartan mein ghusl kya karti thin."
346,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wuzu eik mudd sey aur ghusl paanch mudd sey farma liya kartey they.
347,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, farmati hain ke beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik mudd key sath wuzu kar liya kartey they aur taqriban eik saa key sath ghusl farma liya kartey they."
348,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wuzu eik mudd key sath aur ghusl eik saa sey farma liya kartey they."
